Title: Bucks' Brook Lopez: Puts up 15 points in win
Description: Lopez delivered 15 points (6-11 FG, 2-5 3Pt, 1-1 FT), five rebounds and a steal across 25 minutes in Tuesday's win over the Timberwolves. Lopez was the only Milwaukee starter who didn't play more than 25 minutes,
Author: CBSSports.com
